text: Jaimie Alexander (born March 12, 1984) is an American actress. She played Tammy in It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia. She also played Jenna York in CSI: Miami. The actress was born in Greenville, South Carolina. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from South Carolina Category:1984 births Category:Living people
